**For Etherchannel**
conf t
ip default-gateway xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx
vlan xx
 name xx
int po1
 switchport trunk allowed Vlan add xx
int Vlan xx
 ip address xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx
 no shut 

**For Single Interface**
conf t
ip default-gateway xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx
vlan xx
 name xx
int gi1/0/48
 switchport trunk allowed Vlan add xx
int Vlan xx
 ip address xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx xxx.xxx.xxx.xxx
 no shut 

conf t
default interface Vlan 1
int Vlan 1
 shut
